description.en:
Kirby Inu isn't just some copy cat or fork, it's the presentation of a whole new tokenomics and ecosystem that is brought to life by the developers and supporters of FTP (Fair Token Project).

FTP if you haven't heard consists of the latest technology in the solution of bots that take advantage of your day to day user.

Kirby Inu gives back 10% ETH on total volume, buys or sells. For life. You can claim your rewards from https://app.fairtokenproject.com.
